---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Clay Garden Press
description: Field notes and deep dives. From the bench, not the boardroom.
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1 class="hero-title">Field notes and deep dives.</h1>
  <p class="hero-lede">From the bench, not the boardroom.</p>
</section>

<section class="posts">
  {% if collections.posts.length %}
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <p class="post-card-meta"><time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></p>
        <h2 class="post-card-title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        {% if post.data.description %}<p class="post-card-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
    <p class="empty-state">No posts yet. Building.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
